texts.text: >A temple in the mountains...
>Something scurries about inside the main building...
Hmmm... This is strange...
My sixth sense tells me there's some treasure around here...
...Damn!
Nothing but junk.
But old man Kurama Tengu always tells us to not come here,
and the entrance was sealed as you'd expect, too!
There has to be something here with all that protection... Hey!
>At the foot of an old statue of Buddha is what appears to be a false floor...
Hey hey... Look at that.
This fancy box has the same seal as the one on the entrance!
Haha!
>Koppa Tengu rips off the seal without a second thought!
>...Something stirs inside the box and beings to ooze out!
...Ahh. That blasted seal's been broken.
*Sniff*
*Growl*
Wha...?! What the hell is this?!
It got scary and I hid but...
That box was filled with... Demons?
Even without our master, we're still able to come to life.

Now, it's time to go!
*Laugh*
*Howl*
Are... Are they gone...?
This might be bad? What should I do...?
...Huh, what's the matter?
It's terrible. They're all over the mountain now.
My part too, but they didn't care and trampled all over it.
They kept coming but I managed to take out some of them.
Me too. And then they turned into these strange charms. Look.
This charm...! So, it really is...
Found you! Kurama Tengu!
Hm... Nekomata. You're a rare sight.
Unfortunately, we're in the middle of doing damage control...
I probably want to know the same thing. What the hell's going on?
There was one that looked like folded origami and another that looked like a long dog...
Anyways, I was attacked by these weird things and got separated from Saki!
Since when were those kinds of creatures allowed on your mountain?!
Saki as in your human owner?
You really must like her to be her pet.
Ah, the girl that comes to play every so often.
I keep telling her it's dangerous here,
but she never listens!
It's not that she doesn't listen... I mean, you're...
Shut up, shut up! Now's not the time!
Please explain what's going on and help me find Saki, Kurama Tengu!
What are those things?!
*Nod*
Thanks to all of your information, I now have a better understanding of what's happened.
They are Shikigami demons. Created by man to cause harm to man.
These Shikigami charms made by an Onmyoji, a sorcerer, seem to be propelling them.
They were sealed away in a temple far up the mountain but...
That seal seems to have been broken.
The temple you told us to stay away from, boss?
W-Wait. I think I saw Koppa Tengu snooping around there!
I see... But he already received his punishment.
If these Shikigami reach the human settlements, there will be further trouble.
Sadly, we're in no position to prevent that.
This may be our doing, but all we can do is seal them back into the box...
There's way too many though. It'll take days...
And doesn't that mean that girl's in serious danger?
P-Please, Kurama Tengu. I'll do anything you ask!
Isn't there anything we can do? You're so wise!
...Hmm. You have to break eggs to make an omelet.
I can place a barrier around this mountain and keep any more from escaping.
Oni, Yaksini. Hunt down as many demons as you can.
Yessir!
This should be fun!
Nekomata. You... Go to Akihabara.
Akihabara...?
Akihabara in Tokyo. I hear you'll find a strong group of demon users there.
Go there ask for their assistance.
W-What?! Ask humans?! That sounds...
You know the human world best.
You'll certainly find them the fastest.
It's for Saki's sake. Didn't you just say you'd do anything?
That's not fair...
I mean, how do I even tell them what's going on?
Humans hate demons, so I doubt they'll hear me out...
...I'll leave that to you. Good luck.
...Here? It looks like a regular house...
But the cats around here said this is the place...
Maybe I should change into a human for this...
Can I help you?
Are you okay?
*Scream*
D-Did we surprise you that much...?
This is our Hideout...
Or hang out? One of those things...
Uh, I was...
My name is Miya...
I'm not really used to this so...!
I can't lie either...
You... I mean, are you all part of this group of demon users...?
...! How did you...?
My master, or rumors I mean...? You know...
We're having some trouble with demons and... Uhh...
I need your help no questions asked! Please!
I'm not sure...
Okay.
Yes...
Without any more details, it's going to be difficult with just us...
Wait, Newbie!
You're always doing that! Think these things through a little more!
She's pretty and has great legs, but this sounds shady as hell!
What do her legs have to do with this...?
M-My sister... We were separated in the mountains...
Huh?
And there's a hoard of demons crawling around there now...
So, I beg you...! Please help her...
I guess we can't just leave you like this...
...I don't see why not. The three of us can probably handle it.
We can communicate remotely and react accordingly if it ends up being a trap.
...You're going to help me?
T-Then follow me! I can lead you there!
Interestin'... That's pretty bad yo.
Yes. I understand this is quite a bit to ask of you.
But will you be willing to help us?
This is all very sudden, but we understand the situation now.
Megakin, can we start to hunt these things down and look for Saki?
Yeah, all good.
Let us know if anythin' comes up and you need help.
...It looks like we'll be helping you out.
Thank you.
Bring those charms to me and I will give you some rewards in exchange.
They'll certainly be useful to demon users such as yourselves.
And... Nekomata!
*Gulp*
This bunch doesn't appear to be much inclined to hiking, so go and guide them will you.
And it's long since time you changed back to normal.
You'll have trouble traversing these hills like that too.
What? Nekomata... Change...?

*Sigh*
I hate changing in front of people.
You're a demon...
...Yeah. Got a problem with that?
N-No. Nothing like that.
I have no choice, and don't plan on getting too friendly or anything.
Humans and demons were never meant to get along...
